{
    "tha-ap36:0.1_0": "The senior monks, Householders,",
    "tha-ap36:0.2_0": "Deceivers",
    "tha-ap36:0.3_0": "promption, black-haired in the seniors,",
    "tha-ap36:1.1_0": "“Awakened as a god,",
    "tha-ap36:1.2_0": "the world, for the world of the gods,",
    "tha-ap36:1.3_0": "traveling to the course of time,",
    "tha-ap36:1.4_0": "and wandering towards me.",
    "tha-ap36:10.1_0": "They’ve snarened their own banner,",
    "tha-ap36:10.2_0": "with bright words,",
    "tha-ap36:10.3_0": "Your enemies rejoice;",
    "tha-ap36:10.4_0": "and my family will be safe.",
    "tha-ap36:11.1_0": "After going forth,",
    "tha-ap36:11.2_0": "with bright words,",
    "tha-ap36:11.3_0": "complete understanding",
    "tha-ap36:11.4_0": "will realize quenching.",
    "tha-ap36:12.1_0": "Attaining meditation,",
    "tha-ap36:12.2_0": "their task completed, without defilements,",
    "tha-ap36:12.3_0": "Gotama follows the world,",
    "tha-ap36:12.4_0": "will stand aside.",
    "tha-ap36:13.1_0": "Striving, resolute,",
    "tha-ap36:13.2_0": "peaceful and free of attachments;",
    "tha-ap36:13.3_0": "Udāyī’s called",
    "tha-ap36:13.4_0": "the Teacher is his disciple!’",
    "tha-ap36:14.1_0": "greed, hate, and delusion:",
    "tha-ap36:14.2_0": "along with conceit and contempt,",
    "tha-ap36:14.3_0": "complete understanding",
    "tha-ap36:14.4_0": "and live without defilements.",
    "tha-ap36:15.1_0": "Sumedhā, too,",
    "tha-ap36:15.2_0": "a keen and alert,",
    "tha-ap36:15.3_0": "Purāṇa, the Buddha,",
    "tha-ap36:15.4_0": "I left behind me.",
    "tha-ap36:16.1_0": "Attaining the four kinds of textual analysis",
    "tha-ap36:16.2_0": "... “I attained the noble ones,” ...",
    "tha-ap36:16.3_0": "and fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions.”",
    "tha-ap36:17.1_0": "That is how these verses were recited by the senior venerable Kāḷudāyī.",
    "tha-ap36:18.1_0": "fourth senior,",
    "tha-ap36:2.1_0": "Supassa for the Suppiyā,",
    "tha-ap36:2.2_0": "And a blue lily,",
    "tha-ap36:2.3_0": "Taking the ultimate flame,",
    "tha-ap36:2.4_0": "I gave the Teacher.",
    "tha-ap36:3.1_0": "After eating it, the great hero,",
    "tha-ap36:3.2_0": "he turns into, beautiful, and ugly,",
    "tha-ap36:3.3_0": "I took a flower",
    "tha-ap36:3.4_0": "a person of people.",
    "tha-ap36:4.1_0": "Burded by the world,",
    "tha-ap36:4.2_0": "flowering on flowers,",
    "tha-ap36:4.3_0": "it’s hard to do what it is hard to do,",
    "tha-ap36:4.4_0": "and he gave me a flower.",
    "tha-ap36:5.1_0": "O flowering flowers,",
    "tha-ap36:5.2_0": "with the ultimate goal.",
    "tha-ap36:5.3_0": "I’ll expel them",
    "tha-ap36:5.4_0": "listen to me.",
    "tha-ap36:6.1_0": "‘It’s ten times that I’m a king,",
    "tha-ap36:6.2_0": "They will reduce you to",
    "tha-ap36:6.3_0": "blue water lily,",
    "tha-ap36:6.4_0": "and Mallikā.",
    "tha-ap36:7.1_0": "Bring the result of good deeds,",
    "tha-ap36:7.2_0": "whose divine life is long life,",
    "tha-ap36:7.3_0": "my six-tusked elephant,",
    "tha-ap36:7.4_0": "remember them, they’ll remember them.",
    "tha-ap36:8.1_0": "Twenty-five years have passed",
    "tha-ap36:8.2_0": "and a wheel-turning monarch will become a wheel-turning monarch.",
    "tha-ap36:8.3_0": "kings of the earth,",
    "tha-ap36:8.4_0": "he’ll live his own master.",
    "tha-ap36:9.1_0": "I’m a hundred thousand",
    "tha-ap36:9.2_0": "a family born in this life,",
    "tha-ap36:9.3_0": "Gotama, his clan,",
    "tha-ap36:9.4_0": "The Teacher will be in the world."
}